{"tid":2040310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃絲連登登仔可否理智一點 唔好比人亂帶風","createTime":"2020-05-28T13:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T16:42:00.000Z","uid":255497,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5258e28bbf3305068fa8e61a73dac080c726c13f","tid":2040310,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]呢個post係針對番以下呢個post黎講<br />\n睇完好尷尬先走出黎開post</span><br />\n濫捕學生妹定係幫新屋嶺洗底？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039466</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃絲經常話新屋嶺點樣點樣有幾恐怖<br />\n點樣吹入面有雞姦強姦私刑虐<br />\n咁你有無fc過講呢啲野既人？<br />\n8月11號我係新屋嶺53個其中一位被捕人士<br />\n有親身感受過<br />\n睇到連登fb班黃絲 或者現實見到既人<br />\n都話新屋嶺好恐怖 話班狗係裡面點樣點樣對手足<br />\n我真係唔知笑唔笑好<br />\n唔明點解要炒作呢啲戇鳩未證實新聞<br />\n我同行有6個比狗拉左<br />\n四男兩女 其中有個爆左牙<br />\n爆左牙果個係比狗拉果陣整到<br />\n係新屋嶺等左廿幾個鍾先去醫院<br />\n我同佢一樣都有去求醫都係等左廿幾個鍾<br />\n無可否認狗係有拖延<br />\n但係其他野我就見唔到<br />\n你地問我信唔信入面有手足比人強姦私刑<br />\n我就一定唔信果日有 <br />\n因為事後同行既人一齊轉擔保<br />\n有傾過 入面既氣氛 <br />\n佢地都無發生過奇怪野<br />\n個倉一眼睇晒 有咩人帶走左<br />\n無番到黎大家都知<br />\n大家都可以選擇唔信所見既野<br />\n但係大家都可以諗清楚先<br />\n岩聽既野就聽 唔岩聽就唔聽<br />\n唔肯突破同溫層 唔肯面對事實<br />\n我只想大家諗多啲事實<br />\n唔好人講咩就相信<br />\n好似比人洗晒腦咁<br />\n咁樣同藍絲真係無分別<br />\n最後都係果句啦 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個post預左比人屌話5毛同爆負評屈我係pr狗<br />\n同上個post一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實黃絲同藍絲一樣咁無知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後附上我唔係狗唔係5毛證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（用番上個post既相）<br />\n小弟有份搞上年光復屯門 兩次遊行同85屯門罷工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MygCjM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MygCjM.png&h=33a33fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hu4GOrs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhu4GOrs.jpg&h=3686ca4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK9C6c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK9C6c7.png&h=98ee513f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d211d2bd77b8f974bf1654b6d80fee409fd5766","tid":2040310,"uid":47222,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"你冇事唔代表其他人冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53e88975922fbaee25ae6849d08020db5f96c7e","tid":2040310,"uid":255497,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d211d2bd77b8f974bf1654b6d80fee409fd5766","tid":2040310,"uid":47222,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"你冇事唔代表其他人冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:16:41.000Z","msg":"批判性思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a2d700d20ccd3d45d475420e615a93795b2373","tid":2040310,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係針對番811新屋嶺<br />\n警暴問題大家都知 我唔係話無警暴</span></span>"},{"pid":"98c8c87900e5572fe89196167cd6ebb32d6a6004","tid":2040310,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔岩聽 5毛分化黑警黎<br />\n連登係咪一言堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3250b8db485483fefc27b93944dd3b414ec2b79f","tid":2040310,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d211d2bd77b8f974bf1654b6d80fee409fd5766","tid":2040310,"uid":47222,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"你冇事唔代表其他人冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"講緊8月11當日"},{"pid":"38efa7e21ac91073032ea7ac32ce3c60363c9dab","tid":2040310,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"s